  # **Eventual consistency**: The KMS API follows an eventual consistency
  # model. For more information, see [KMS eventual consistency][6].
  #
  #
  #
  # [1]: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/nitro-enclave.html
