  #
  # * [kms:UpdateAlias][3] on the new KMS key (key policy).
  #
  # For details, see [Controlling access to aliases][4] in the *Key
  # Management Service Developer Guide*.
  #
  # **Related operations:**
  #
  # * CreateAlias
  #
